Shortcuts
⌘/CTRL (Meta)When pressed, toggles to Drag / Select or Bounding Box / Polygon.
B Bounding Box tool.
P Polygon tool.
D Drag / Select tool.
N Mark Null tool.

• If the image is already marked as Null, this marks it as Unannotated if it's in the Annotating queue.

+Zooms in.
- Zooms out.
0(Zero) Resets zoom and fits image to screen.
1 Zooms to 100%.
ESC(Escape) Exits the Annotation tool.
←(Left)Navigates to previous image.
→(Right)Navigates to next image.

WHEN AN ANNOTATION IS SELECTED :

ENTERSaves selection and any changes made to the label.
ESC(Escape)Cancels any changes made and deselects.

• If selection was just drawn, deletes selection.

↑(Up)Changes label to the previous classname.
↓(Down)Changes label to the next classname.
BACKSPACEIf no label is assigned, deletes the selection.

• To delete a selection : clear label(one backspace), and hit backspace(two backspaces total).

IN REVIEW MODE :

A Approves annotation
R Rejects annotation
